{"Name":"Keystone@Mandai","ShortName":"Keystone@Mandai","Description":"Keystone @ Mandai is a freehold B2 industrial development located at 2C Mandai Estate, offering a rare opportunity in a mature industrial precinct. The project comprises 69 units of various sizes ranging from 1,658 to 2,024 sqft, ideal for operations such as light industrial, logistics, production and packaging. With its freehold tenure and strategic location, it combines long-term asset value with strong connectivity to major expressways.","StartUrl":"/","Display":"standalone","BackgroundColor":"#ffffff","ThemeColor":"#041e42","Orientation":"portrait","Icons":[{"Src":"https://rtdbookappointment.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/Bookappointment/Property/8689317f-2253-4b50-b1ca-b1cd600f06a5","Sizes":"192x192","Type":"image/png"},{"Src":"https://rtdbookappointment.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/Bookappointment/Property/8689317f-2253-4b50-b1ca-b1cd600f06a5","Sizes":"512x512","Type":"image/png"}]}